Reason for opening the vacancy:The need to expand the team due to the increase in the number of projectsStructure of the company:The company has two offices, 45 employees work in Khmelnitsky, 22 employees in Kiev. We are engaged in expansion of teams in two offices, also we work on a remote basis with specialists from other regions of Ukraine. Company structure: CEO, management (head of the office and 4 project managers), team: web, mobile, design, QA, sales, marketing, HR & Recruiting, back office.Our benefits and working conditions:Our benefits and working conditions:
Working timetable: from 9.00 to 18.00 or from 10.00 to 19.00
