We are regular partners and sponsors of fwdays conferences: https://fwdays.com
We organize and conduct meetups where we discuss various topics that may be interesting for the IT community: http://meetups.stfalcon.com/
We develop projects with free source code and open source solutions: github.com/stfalcon-studio
